quran[56]{c,v,t}:
  74,1,ohiweamenewakutidwa
  74,2,Dzukandikuperekachenjezo
  74,3,Ndipo lemekeza Ambuye wako
  74,4,Ndipo yeretsa zovala zako
  74,5,Ndipo pewa zonse za mafano
  74,6,Ndipo usapereke thandizo ndi cholinga chopezamo cholowa
  74,7,Ndipo khala wopirira chifukwa cha Ambuye wako
  74,8,Ndipo pamene lipenga lidzalira
  74,9,Ndithudi limeneli lidzakhala tsiku loopsa
  74,10,Tsiku lamavuto kwa anthu onse osakhulupirira
  74,11,Ndisiye ndekha kuthana ndi munthu amene ndidamulenga ndekha
  74,12,Ndipo ndidamupatsa chuma chosawerengeka
  74,13,Ndi ana okhala pambali pake
  74,14,Ndipo Ine ndidamuchitira zonse kuti zikhale zolongosoka ndi zapafupi
  74,15,Koma nthawi zonse amafuna kuti ndizimupatsabe zinthu zambiri
  74,16,Kosatheka! Ndithudi iye wakhala ali kuchitira mwano chivumbulutso chathu
  74,17,Ine ndidzamukhaulitsa pomupatsa chilango chowawa
  74,18,Ndithudi iye adaganiza ndipo adakonza chiwembu
  74,19,Ndipo ayenera kutembererewa chifukwa cha chiwembu chake
  74,20,Motero iye ayenera kutembereredwa chifukwa cha chiwembu chake
  74,21,Ndipo iye anayang’ana
  74,22,Ndipo iye adachita matsinya ndipo anaonetsa kuipidwa
  74,23,Kenaka adatembenukira kumbali modzikweza
  74,24,"Ndipo iye adati: “Ichi sichina koma matsenga a anthu a amakedzana!”"
  74,25,“Ichi sichina koma mawu a munthu chabe.”
  74,26,Ine ndidzamuponya iye ku Gahena
  74,27,Kodi chidzakudziwitsa kuti moto wa ku Gahena ndi chiani
  74,28,Iwo susunga kapena kusiya
  74,29,Umatentha matupi
  74,30,Umasamalidwandiangelokhumindiasanundianayi
  74,31,"Ife sitidasankhe wina aliyense koma angelo kuti aziyang’anira moto ndipo tinakhazikitsa chiwerengero chawo ngati mayesero kwa anthu osakhulupirira, kuti iwo onse amene alandira mawu a Mulungu akhulupirire ndi kuti anthu okhulupirira m’choonadi apitirize chikhulupiriro chawo; kuti iwo amene adalandira kale mawu a Mulungu ndiponso anthu onse okhulupirira moona asakhale ndi chikaiko china chilichonse; ndipo kuti onse amene m’mitima mwawo muli matenda pamodzi ndi anthu osakhulupirira anganene kuti: “Kodi Mulungu afuna kutanthauza chiyani pa chitsanzo chotere?” Mmenemo ndi mmene Mulungu amasokeretsera munthu aliyense amene Iye wamufuna ndi kutsogolera aliyense amene Iye wamufuna. Palibe munthu amene amadziwa asirikali a Ambuye wako kupatula Iye mwini. Ichi si china chilichonse koma chikumbutso kwa anthu onse"
  74,32,"Iyayi, ndilumbira pali mwezi"
  74,33,Ndi pali usiku pamene uli n’kutha
  74,34,Ndi pali m’mbandakucha pamene uli n’kudza
  74,35,Ndithudi ili ndi limodzi la masoka akuluakulu
  74,36,Ndi chenjezo kwa anthu onse
  74,37,Kwa yense wa inu amene afuna kupitirirabe mtsogolo kapena afuna kutsalira m’mbuyo
  74,38,Munthu aliyense adzafunsidwa molingana ndi ntchito zake
  74,39,Kupatula iwo amene adzakhala kudzanja lamanja
  74,40,"M’minda, iwo azidzafunsana wina ndi mnzake. Qiyamah"
  74,41,Za anthu ochimwa kuti
  74,42,Kodi ndi chiyani chimene chakulowetsani inu ku moto
  74,43,"Iwo adzayankha nati: “Ife sitimapemphera.”"
  74,44,Ndiponso sitimadyetsa anthu a njala
  74,45,Ife timangotsutsa zinthu mwaumbuli
  74,46,Ndipo tidali kunena kuti kulibe tsiku lachiweruzo
  74,47,Mpaka pamene imfa idatipeza
  74,48,Motero palibe chidandaulo chochokera kwa wina aliyense chimene chidzamveka
  74,49,Kodindichifukwachiyaniiwoalikuthawachikumbutso ichi
  74,50,Monga abulu odzidzimutsidwa
  74,51,"omwe anali kuthawa Mlenje, Mkango kapena nyama ina yoopsya"
  74,52,Iai! Aliyense wa iwo afuna kuti apatsidwe masamba a Buku otambasula
  74,53,Ndikosatheka! Koma iwo alibe mantha ndi zimene zili nkudza
  74,54,Iyayi. Ndithudi ili ndi chenjezo
  74,55,Motero musiyeni amene afuna kuti awerenge ndi kulandira chenjezo
  74,56,"Ndipo iwo sadzalandira chenjezo pokha pokha ngati Mulungu afuna. Iye ndiye Ambuye wofunika kuti anthu onse azichita mantha ndi Iye, ndipo Iye ndi Ambuye wokhululukira"